||   C*
|+---C           S@PROC    WHEQ 'DATA'
||   C                     EXSR #DATA
||   C*
|E---C                     ENDSL
|    C*
E----C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C*==<END PGM   >==*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C*
     C*****************************************************
