     C                     EXFMTECSPW751
     C*                    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
     C                     TIME           S@TIME
     C*
     C*==<NEXT    >==*
S----C                     SELEC
+----C           *IN01     WHEQ '1'                        < F1 >
|    C                     MOVEL'EXIT'    S@PROC
|    C*
